modName: Non God Near God Start Game Booster
summary:
If you have beaten the main game and you want your character to have the atributes of your last character, plus a little more.
This will save you from typing 50+ codes indavidually, and having to remember the codes.
descriptionHtml:
If you have beaten the main game and you want your character to have the atributes of your last character, plus a little more.
100 to all skills, all perks, $9000000 gold, 500 lockpicks, all spells (Dragon Shouts not inc), 10 Dragon Souls, smithery items, can run twice as fast!
You are not immortal, but this is best used on the hardest dificulty setting.
If you like it please endorse :)
This will save you from typing 50+ codes indavidually, and having to remember the codes.
author: AbleOne
